		{
			description: [
				"So, you wish to learn the art of occultism? You wish to summon demons to do your bidding? Very well. I will teach you what I know."
				"&o&6Occultism&r is a mod based around drawing pentacles and sacrifcing items to summon demons for a variety of different tasks. It allows for a unique form of automation utilizing mobs and not blocks. The mod also features ways to get specific drops earlier than usual."
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"To begin, you will want &oDemon's Dream&r, a new crop that forms a base for future actions. Seeds can be found by breaking grass."
