				"You've obtained your book and some Demon's Dream. Now you are ready to gain materials from &othe Otherworld&r."
				"&o&6Ignite a Demon's Dream with Flint and Steel&r to create Spiritfire. Worry not about burns, for these purple flames have no heat. Rather, they will connect you to the Otherworld and &o&6exchange items thrown in&r."
